social_posts.post_text:
Silipin natin ang Nuestra Señora del Patrocinio de Maria Church also known as Boljoon Church.. Built in 1599 and one of the oldest Augustinian churches in Cebu next to the Church of Santo Niño in Cebu City. The 424 year old parish is made of coral stones, making it the oldest standing stone church in the Philippines.
